p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Checks if the date is between two other dates
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
Checks if the date is between the two other dates (limits included)
**Note:** Make sure that the data type is converted to Date/Time for this brick to work properly.
**Example**:
Can use "String to Datetime" when getting the data from a text field to convert the string into datetime
The date to be checked if it is in between or not
The start date of the range to check
The end date of the range to check
Returns `True` if it is in between, `False` otherwise.
